name: extreme_with_dependency_order_four
section: binding-scope-deep
args: a:Int b:Int c:Int d:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Lexical binding and shadowing must preserve dependency order and branch-local scope.
law: (with [x (+ {a} {b})] (with [y (- {c} {d})] (with [z (* x y)] (= z (* (+ {a} {b}) (- {c} {d}))))))
